{
  "stem": "9538.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so had other transports.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They say that in the forest of Riga there are 80,000 Jewish souls.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the meantime, we had a relatively proper hospital in Riga.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had supplies to come in from the outside, which was allowed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "See, we all-- they formed groups that worked in Riga of the prisoners, of the Jews.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some worked for the SS, some worked for the Wehrmacht-- that means the German army.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some worked for civilian firms.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some worked at the harbors-- you know, import, exports to help, like, dockers that worked, like, dockers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they lived in the ghetto, came back at night, were marched out in the morning with-- under SS-- being accompanied by SS or Wehrmacht, or German Wehrmacht.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It depends which units they were working for.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so those people, under risk of their own life, brought in food in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were exchanging food at work places-- clothing for food, because we found clothes from the poor Latvian Jews.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they took these clothes out into their work places and traded them in, under fear of their own life, with the Latvian civilian people, and smuggled food into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And of course, if it was found on you, it was the end of your life.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Under risk of life, they smuggled food in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The people-- eventually, it got a little bit more normal.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I mean, if you can say it, that it got normal.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But people had a little bit more to eat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We had a hospital.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And there were doctors-- Latvian Jewish doctors-- working at a pharmaceutical firm in Riga.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And under risk of their own lives, they smuggled medicines in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we had surgical instruments.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
